2013;;Hansel & Gretel;;American;;Anthony C. Ferrante;;Dee Wallace, Brent Lydic, Stephanie Greco, Steve Hanks, Clark Perry;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hansel_%26_Gretel_(2013_film);;Teen siblings Hansel and Gretel Grimm are abducted by an elderly recluse named Lilith and witness the horrors of her home in the woods. Lilith and her moronic sons are involved in a conspiracy to fatten up children before she eats them and the local population to serve in meat pies in her local shop "the Gingerbread House". The plot revolves around their attempts to escape the clutches of this old age pensioner, and her mute sons.